Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Herme's的传单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家平价百货店的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 他们家今天开始特别促销
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里能买到福音想要的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.28,0:00:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要买「世界和平」是不太可能了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道哪里有卖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槽点太多不知从何吐起呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲有什么想要的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前没有想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有什么必需品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装备和备份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 我们去找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗 克拉玲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再啰嗦一句
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以去危险的地方呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.69,0:00:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓少女 仅仅存在于此 便已是一种危险
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.61,0:01:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃至凶器...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.07,0:01:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布耶尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本店Herme's正在举行开业三周年庆典
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便宜便宜 总之就是便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为盛大活动的一环
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日将举办最新防灾物资展销会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比利 不要乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里好厉害啊 克拉玲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我们从最上面一层开始逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定会有克拉玲想要的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闻到了 能闻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚民们的物欲卷起了漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正可谓凶器...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来容我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日起开始举办的特别促销活动的一日店长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞南库尔岛议会议长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢各位今天聚集于此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我就是这座岛的议长 杰纳斯·诺斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这绝不仅是一家百货店的大促销
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更是对前几日在瓦尔甘地区发生的恐怖袭击事件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及近日成为严重问题的通信故障的应对方案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Herme's不仅常备食品和饮用水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:04:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更有燃料 电源等无间断供应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且 一旦发生紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些物资将免费提供给岛民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于本人诺斯和议会提出的这个划时代措施
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提供了大力协助的Herme's百货店 我衷心表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面将由以议长为原型的吉祥物 诺斯君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为议长献上花束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺斯君 Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一刻终于到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺斯议长 关于您奢侈的私生活和豪宅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及连这家Herme's的停车场都停不下的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级豪华奢华特别定制高级轿车的购买等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对多方质疑 对此您有什么想说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,质疑？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤明的岛民可不希望一个穷酸相的负责人去进行外交
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您闭嘴 议长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你诚心诚意地问了 那我就大发慈悲告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正是此时此刻抓住了独家新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踏上了通向明星殿堂的红毯（预定）的未来型报道偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫布玲...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲 为什么不能坐那边的漂亮电梯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看到外面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怕高吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从安全方面考虑 不建议乘坐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防被狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于50口径的子弹 强化玻璃也是无用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那是在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在众多媒体面前真是失礼至极
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 似乎是自由记者混了进来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位去几层？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去能吃炒面的楼层
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20层
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是高级机器人 还有2台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为到处用这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们都被抢走了饭碗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经济变得不景气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媒体会炸开锅的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之第五足低声私语
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传达着不祥之事攀附的混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这个是那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感受 沸腾 要迸发了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正乃通信故障是也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 又通信故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓了 反正现在已经没有新闻价值了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过要是能独家拍到发生原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定能拿到局长奖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数据传输中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么搞的 给我想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火灾 这可是独家新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位顾客 现在发布一则通知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本商业区现在发生了通信故障
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次故障会造成多少经济损失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议长 我们回议事总部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到捐款才优待了这家店 这下不是面子丢光了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议长 我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您再这么口无遮拦 我就得给您一发电击了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.62,0:07:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通信故障时的机器人和自动贩卖机没什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意 它们的行为和记录功能都受到了限制
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那请您再冷静些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通信故障还有30分钟左右就会恢复了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议长？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在有紧急问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小问题 还是大问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求助 求助 求助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了紧急事态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警卫室 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 连不上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议长 您还能撑多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10 不 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议长 请用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好这里只有我和机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦撑不住了就...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 关于这件事...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是人类哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太失礼了 这位女士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这座岛的议长 杰纳斯·诺斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是七转福音 也请你多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了维持表面冷静 加重了内心负担
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上到临界点了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缓缓吸气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您撑住啊 议长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潘多拉装置 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解码技能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃尔维斯系列
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治愈空间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心灵 痛苦 都被治愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲伤的记忆都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议长 你没事吧议长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这...会不会只是气体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定松开一下的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议 议长 在出去前还请您忍耐 不要放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厕 厕 厕 厕所～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正可谓黄金之时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个地方真黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里好像能打开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会答谢...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No一一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支援还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 由于通信故障指挥系统现在一片混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自动灭火器和火警都没动静？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位观众请看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百货店Herme's正在燃烧坍塌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现场混乱到了极点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟为什么会发展成这样的事态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是有人故意放火？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是恐怖分子干的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们 在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议长 这里走不通了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避难是不是已经结束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火警也没响啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲 很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面一层的楼梯还完好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实到了那里 就应该能逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 要是我年轻个20岁的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能飞过去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不应该产生有毒气体的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直被这么熏呛的话会窒息的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 你叫福音对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有发现绳索或绳梯之类的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 你们在这里等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先去寻找逃下去的路线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议长 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来没法穿过这片卖场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防火墙内部温度在300摄氏度以上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下方楼层平均温度约为400度 并且正在上升
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 凭福音和克拉里昂的耐久性 可以突破
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建议迅速避难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 克拉玲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议长先生他们还没逃出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救出2人的可能性非常低
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有什么办法 能让家一起逃出去的...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲 帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潘多拉装置 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解码技能 埃尔维斯系列
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女装设计师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺斯议长 那边的楼梯被火包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 我决不能死在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想和议长一起死啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 没什么办法下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 你们还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心别咬到舌头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲 路上没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 但是噪音很多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视觉化处理运行负担很重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我这边来处理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回音定位法？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是指把声音视觉化的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没有器材的情况下是怎么做到的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没氧气了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这样你们就...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们靠体内的氧气还能再撑一会儿 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 报告说有适合者移居到了这个岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道就是这些孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警告 前方出现障碍物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这就是 全世界仅有数例的...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功的全身义体？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就算是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能在人类和机械间如此自由切换吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了 没想到真的到达了安全楼梯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是七转福音和克拉玲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是克拉里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细一看好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建议迅速避难
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你看 能不能也把那孩子带上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不救救他的话 那孩子会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的行动是最优选项的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并不是福音的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊 我想大家一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按现在的燃烧状态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这幢建筑物的建材撑不了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有产生可燃性气体的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请立刻避难
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲你先逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去救那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比利 比利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁去救救我家孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有生还者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议长 幸好您没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多 多亏了我平时积德多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不说这个 和我们一起逃生的少女们在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们是我们的救命恩人 两人都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃出来的只有你们两位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 明明是一起逃出来的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样 七转福音君 克拉玲君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音君 克拉玲君？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点 已经没事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位请退后 这里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.06,0:18:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楼梯塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氧气瓶的余量不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强制排出我体内的氧气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样暂时就能...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 我施展过魔咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定能得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氧气的消耗已经...但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:19:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救以后 一定要向克拉玲道歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没找到想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是克拉玲...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲 你的耳朵焦了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明叫你先逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音的生命是最优先的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会救小孩的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那福音想怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 想救这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 照那个速度...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲 一定要大家一起逃出去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给急救队 一定要救活他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到需救护人员了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一名小孩 一名女性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位母亲 没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比利 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音君 克拉玲君 为了救我们...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议长 那两个人平安无事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 小孩也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 克拉玲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该道歉的是克拉里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.66,0:21:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音的判断是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我们再去...买克拉玲想要的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这双腿已经无法再前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在原地寻求救援更为明智
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驳回 治疗福音是最优先的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚和你们说过不要去危险的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就弄成了这幅样子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.33,0:22:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克鲁茨上校 布耶尔已经稳定下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打个喷嚏就能变成这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.38,0:22:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事对CDF保持绝密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.31,0:23:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的高级轿车
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.61,0:23:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,压坏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.73,0:23:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.23,0:24:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的记者们 问题一个一个来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.19,0:24:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是希望的偶像报道员 布玲一一
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.53,0:24:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.45,0:24:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕她
